# AuroraOS extras — Wayland kiosk stack + Firefox GTK3 runtime deps (BLFS-style)
# Built in dependency order by 10-aurora-shell.sh. URLs track BLFS 12.3 versions;
# if one 404s, bump to the current release on the same site.

